      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Honest Value & Ready to Ride \u2013 A Solid Fair-Condition Find! \ud83d\ude99\n\nLooking for a practical, budget-friendly vehicle that gets the job done? This one might be just what you need! We'll be completely upfront: this car is in fair condition, meaning it has some visible wear and minor imperfections that come with its age and use \u2014 but it runs and drives, making it a great option for a savvy buyer. It's priced to reflect its true condition, so you're getting real value without any surprises. If you're after an affordable daily driver and appreciate straight-talking sellers, come take a look \u2014 we'd love to find this car a good home! \ud83d\ude4c",
