    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture of what to expect. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a solid shine with only minor surface blemishes such as small scuffs or light scratches consistent with normal everyday use. There are no significant dents or structural concerns. The interior is clean and functional, showing moderate wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, this car has been maintained and runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts properly, and all major systems are in good working order. You may find minor cosmetic imperfections here and there, but overall this is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been well cared for. A great choice for a buyer looking for genuine value without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, offering dependable everyday transportation with a well-maintained overall presentation. The exterior shows minor cosmetic blemishes \u2014 think small surface scratches or light scuffs consistent with normal use \u2014 but no significant damage, rust, or structural concerns. The paint retains a respectable appearance and the body panels align properly. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional; upholstery shows moderate wear in high-contact areas but nothing torn or heavily soiled. Mechanically, the car has been looked after \u2014 the engine starts reliably, runs smoothly, and all major systems (brakes, transmission, cooling, electrical) are in good working order. Tires have reasonable tread remaining. This is a solid, honest used car that will serve its next owner well without requiring immediate repairs \u2014 a great choice for a buyer who wants reliable transportation at a fair price.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're pleased to present an honest and thorough picture of what you'll be getting. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a nice shine and the body panels are in solid shape, though if you look closely you may notice a few minor scratches or small scuffs consistent with normal everyday use. There are no significant dents or rust concerns to report, and the car presents respectably from a distance and up close. The interior is clean and well-maintained \u2014 the seats show only light, expected wear, the dashboard and trim pieces are intact, and all major controls function as they should. You won't find any torn upholstery or broken components here. Mechanically, this car has been kept in good working order \u2014 the engine starts reliably, runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts without issue. Brakes, suspension, and steering all feel solid and responsive. We do recommend, as with any used vehicle, that you have your own mechanic perform an inspection before purchase, but we're confident you'll find this car to be exactly as described. This is a dependable, presentable vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34000.0,
